Package: visualOptimization
Type: Package
Title: Visualize Classical Root-finding Algorithm for Optimization
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zirui Li
Maintainer: Zirui Li <luiselzr104566@gmail.com>
Description: In numeric optimization task, it is crutial to find roots for the first derivative of given function. 
    This package visualizes the root finding process of Newton-Raphson method and Secant method to 
    help the beginners understand how these algorithms work.
